The Cartographer has an open commission for a complete survey of the Lost City ruins. The site is of significant geographic and historical interest, and the Cartographer's archive holds only fragmentary records of its current accessible layout. Survey every traversable section of the ruins and return with a complete navigation record suitable for the geographic reference collection.
